{"tid":675921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美駐華外交官稱聞怪聲致腦創傷　王毅否認聲波干擾籲勿政治化","createTime":"2018-05-24T03:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T06:24:45.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed3cf64dbacfad6bc304ac335ba592635ae3589","tid":675921,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美駐華外交官稱聞怪聲致腦創傷　王毅否認聲波干擾籲勿政治化</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國一名在駐廣州總領事館工作的美國人，早前稱受到異常聲音和壓力影響，回國檢查後發現出現輕度腦部創傷。美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，美方關注是次「嚴重醫學事件」，在醫學上與美國駐古巴外交人員2016年底遭音波攻擊導致腦受損一事相似。剛巧在華盛頓會晤蓬佩奧的國務委員兼外長王毅則表示，未發現有任何組織或個人進行聲波干擾，不希望事件被放大、複雜化和政治化。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐北京大使館周三（23日）表示，一名被派到廣州總領事館的美國公民由去年底至今年4月，出現連串「身體徵狀」，包括「輕微但不尋常的聲音和壓力感覺」，經檢查後發現出現輕度腦創傷，但認為與古巴事件無關。<br />\n<br />\n身在華府的蓬佩奧稱，美國關注是次「嚴重醫學事件」，已當面向來訪的王毅提及此事，並正聯同中方調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n王毅則表示，將繼續以外交渠道與美方溝通，並建議美國進行相應的內部調查，承諾中方會保障駐華外交人員的權益，「我們很負責任進行了調查，沒有發現任何組織任何個人來做這種所謂的聲波來干擾的事情」。他說不希望這宗個別事件被放大、複雜化和政治化。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180524/s00005/1527123715329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180524%2Fs00005%2F1527123715329&d=24PkLJ6Ty%2FO0VFS1NGPvh8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2399f158\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180524%2Fs00005%2F1527123715329&h=c531f491\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180524/s00005/1527123715329</a>"},{"pid":"a4015b331c405330d093c5ed0c0747fb5683aee1","tid":675921,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4195fce540abb892064e8de75ff1ba3dbbaad8b","tid":675921,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"沒事兒，沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebc188f80cf6d5abe498508770aa8b1299a1cf2","tid":675921,"uid":176442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"勿政治化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf512e2bcacc9912983725a4164dd0cfa686de0","tid":675921,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"唔想政治化又由佢講出黎？是但搵個城管講都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80c04f6e37d06dbfe79cf74f683366b61fb8825","tid":675921,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"貿易戰贏咗<br />\n今次連外交官都攪埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n贏國終於勃起了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845efff9a4f327ecb64c68f0b702f4ba83113581","tid":675921,"uid":131157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"其實好撚恐怖，手法好低莊"},{"pid":"e921e72cb0794a45cd75a70752c3d576265d2891","tid":675921,"uid":50386,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"美國都冇指名道姓話邊個做<br />\n反而王偽自己心虛衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d7cdc9dd43800f81b741995d6b34616f43c387","tid":675921,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"845efff9a4f327ecb64c68f0b702f4ba83113581","tid":675921,"uid":131157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"其實好撚恐怖，手法好低莊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:14:31.000Z","msg":"支那人好恐怖"},{"pid":"5458a3c79ac485f1d837a757fc58095679e1cfb0","tid":675921,"uid":10937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"起香港都有用，支那狗真係全世界最賤"},{"pid":"ffc0bfeae0066fcdfcc296a8a6224866dfa6347d","tid":675921,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:24:17.000Z"